{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0339e1b1-2b53-40d8-8044-137cb9a5cb0c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0339e1b1-2b53-40d8-8044-137cb9a5cb0c@3.pkg/1772602366768/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602367399", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0339e1b1-2b53-40d8-8044-137cb9a5cb0c@3.pkg/1772602366768/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602367399"}, "identifier": "0339e1b1-2b53-40d8-8044-137cb9a5cb0c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】诗《次北固山下》中秋雁北归，所以，是有雁可托。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】次北固山下 王湾</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>客路青山外，行舟绿水前。潮平两岸阔，风正一帆悬。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>海日生残夜，江春入旧年。乡书何处达？归雁洛阳边。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】章台夜思 韦庄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>清瑟怨遥夜，绕弦风雨哀。孤灯闻楚角，残月下章台。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>芳草已云暮，故人殊未来。乡书不可寄，秋雁又南回。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①章台：即章华台，是古代楚国的离宫。②瑟：古代弦乐器。多为二十五弦。弦乐器，这里指乐声。清瑟，即凄清的瑟声。③楚角：楚地的角声。角是古代军中的乐器。④殊：竟，尚。</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】次北固山下 王湾客路青山外，行舟绿水前。潮平两岸阔，风正一帆悬。海日生残夜，江春入旧年。乡书何处达？归雁洛阳边。【乙】章台夜思 韦庄清瑟怨遥夜，绕弦风雨哀。孤灯闻楚角，残月下章台。芳草已云暮，故人殊未来。乡书不可寄，秋雁又南回。【注释】①章台：即章华台，是古代楚国的离宫。②瑟：古代弦乐器。多为二十五弦。弦乐器，这里指乐声。清瑟，即凄清的瑟声。③楚", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0339e1b1-2b53-40d8-8044-137cb9a5cb0c@3.pkg/item.json?v=1751941784540", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《次北固山下》开头两句点题。&ldquo;客路&rdquo;即驿道，既在青山之外，可见这是诗人的想象。而颔联则写船上所见景色。先写&ldquo;客路&rdquo;后写&ldquo;行舟&rdquo;，漂泊羁旅之情流露于字里行间。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《章台夜思》的颔联以繁笔铺陈，用&ldquo;孤灯&rdquo;&ldquo;楚角&rdquo;&ldquo;残月&rdquo;&ldquo;章台&rdquo;等常见意象加以层层渲染，突出&ldquo;夜思&rdquo;之苦。这联对仗工稳，余味无穷。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首诗都是羁旅之人的怀乡之作，都饱含了旅人的异乡孤独悲凉之情，而《次北固山下》一诗借海&ldquo;日&rdquo;初升和江上早&ldquo;春&rdquo;的美景，还表达了诗人积极向上的乐观情感。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首诗的尾联都用&ldquo;雁足传书&rdquo;的故事寄托了思乡之情，又都抒发了诗人因秋雁南回，无雁可托，使得家书无法寄回的悲苦。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】次北固山下 王湾</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>客路青山外，行舟绿水前。潮平两岸阔，风正一帆悬。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>海日生残夜，江春入旧年。乡书何处达？归雁洛阳边。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】章台夜思 韦庄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>清瑟怨遥夜，绕弦风雨哀。孤灯闻楚角，残月下章台。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>芳草已云暮，故人殊未来。乡书不可寄，秋雁又南回。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①章台：即章华台，是古代楚国的离宫。②瑟：古代弦乐器。多为二十五弦。弦乐器，这里指乐声。清瑟，即凄清的瑟声。③楚角：楚地的角声。角是古代军中的乐器。④殊：竟，尚。</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "0339e1b1-2b53-40d8-8044-137cb9a5cb0c", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】次北固山下 王湾客路青山外，行舟绿水前。潮平两岸阔，风正一帆悬。海日生残夜，江春入旧年。乡书何处达？归雁洛阳边。【乙】章台夜思 韦庄清瑟怨遥夜，绕弦风雨哀。孤灯闻楚角，残月下章台。芳草已云暮，故人殊未来。乡书不可寄，秋雁又南回。【注释】①章台：即章华台，是古代楚国的离宫。②瑟：古代弦乐器。多为二十五弦。弦乐器，这里指乐声。清瑟，即凄清的瑟声。③楚"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】次北固山下 王湾</span>